  "text": "Note that the antisymmetrized projection of the Halperin (551) state has been considered previously [CITATION_1] , although it was not formally identified as the fermionic Haffnian state. It is interesting to note that there is also a similar connection between the MR Pfaffian state and the antisymmetrized projection of the Halperin (331) state [CITATION_2] :",
